{"id":963373888,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 weeks, 3 days","timestamp":1685848708,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"23 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/963373888/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sum of Matrix After Queries","memory":"74 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public long matrixSumQueries(int n, int[][] q){\n        HashSet<Integer> colhs=new HashSet<>();\n        HashSet<Integer> rowhs=new HashSet<>();\n       \n        long ans=0;\n        for(int i=q.length-1;i>=0;i--){\n            if(q[i][0]==1){\n                int col=q[i][1];\n                int val=q[i][2];\n                if(!colhs.contains(col)){\n                    ans+=(n-rowhs.size())*val;\n                    colhs.add(col);  \n                }\n            }\n            else{\n                int row=q[i][1];\n                int val=q[i][2];\n                if(!rowhs.contains(row)){\n                    ans+=(n-colhs.size())*val;\n                    rowhs.add(row);\n                }\n                \n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sum-of-matrix-after-queries","has_notes":false}
